title: BNB price range, Feb 18th?
question: BNB price range, Feb 18th?
description:
## Resolution Criteria:
This market resolves to the range of the "Close" price for the Binance 1-minute candle for BNB/USDT at Feb 18th, 11:59pm UTC.

## Resolution Sources:
The resolution source for this market is Binance, specifically the BNB/USDT "Close" prices available on [Binance](https://www.binance.com/en/trade/BNB_USDT?type=spot) with the "1m" and "Candles" selected on the top bar.

## Additional Information:
Please note that the outcome of this market depends solely on the price data from the Binance BNB/USDT trading pair. Prices from other exchanges, different trading pairs, or spot markets will not be considered for resolution. This market will be resolved within 24 hours after the index timestamp.*
